{"tid":733261,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打既女朋友好錫自己？","createTime":"2018-07-07T15:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T02:17:28.000Z","uid":92132,"like":20,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"491dba039143d1a5f2cc293f8c320f4cbd04ba69","tid":733261,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"拍左就黎半年拖 呢次已經係第三次拍拖<br />\n我都已經25歲<br />\n幸福既程度簡直同以往比唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女朋友21歲 但感情方面好成熟 好貼地 <br />\n佢知道單靠一個人可能無可能買樓 <br />\n所以將來會選擇同我一齊儲錢 供樓<br />\n每次我工作壓力大 佢都會有方法令我減壓 <br />\n有時我扮下小朋友 對住佢唱給我o泡 給我o泡 都唔會覺得我on9 <br />\n覺得呢種係釋放壓力既一種方法<br />\n佢又會願意同我晚晚打機<br />\n佢又會遠離其他異性<br />\n有時又會送小禮物比我 <br />\n仲會每日朝早打電話叫我起身返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時我都會自卑mode 咁話 <br />\n我又矮又窮又唔靚仔 點解你要選擇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知佢話 呢d咪真愛囉 <br />\n有時真係會頂唔住對佢眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲將最重要既野比埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愛你呀 女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c18f9cb507c82eba142875da3c6311edac5f039","tid":733261,"uid":151664,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:17:13.000Z","msg":"可惜你女朋友係有賓周嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c292339674e975bac8a9ca804409a3186feb94","tid":733261,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c18f9cb507c82eba142875da3c6311edac5f039","tid":733261,"uid":151664,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:17:13.000Z","msg":"可惜你女朋友係有賓周嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T15:19:16.000Z","msg":"無賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驗過"},{"pid":"0389f8224d27bcbdeca5b2d7565e64e741dbb008","tid":733261,"uid":121060,"like":9,"dislike":0